{
 "file": "_STGSP4B.bin",
 "source_size": 39600,
 "built_size": 42341,
 "edits": [
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x43aa",
   "jp_len": 8,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "啊啊！？",
   "zh_hex": "15e7c3e7c3ef9705000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x43e2",
   "jp_len": 14,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "不好！……贝拉！！",
   "zh_hex": "15e7b5e7c7ef970909e857e7c2ef97ef970000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x539a",
   "jp_len": 18,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "是吗……他们终于还是动手了……",
   "zh_hex": "15e7b6e8020909e80ce7bbe8e2e879e7f7e7b6ef30ef66e7ba090900000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x53c7",
   "jp_len": 15,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "嗯、不会有错的、金凯度",
   "zh_hex": "15e86502e7b5e7e2e7cbe885e7b402e902e95fe96d000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x53fa",
   "jp_len": 16,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "终于、到了该回归的时刻了吗……",
   "zh_hex": "15e8e2e87902e7d7e7bae898ef52e947e7b4ef2de91fe7bae802090900000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x5425",
   "jp_len": 26,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "……十字先锋、要回归它本来的样子了",
   "zh_hex": "150909ea4ae980ef8be96702ef2aef52e947e978efa6efcfe7b4e7dae886e7ba0000000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x5463",
   "jp_len": 11,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "什、什么！？",
   "zh_hex": "15e7dd02e7dde7bdef97050000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x5490",
   "jp_len": 13,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "是、是宇宙海盗！！",
   "zh_hex": "15e7b602e7b6e8bee8bfe91be9f3ef97ef970000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x54c9",
   "jp_len": 24,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "我、我们可是非武装的运输舰啊……！",
   "zh_hex": "15efcc02efcce7bbe7c4e7b6e8f0e8ece98fe7b4e986e8b9e7d4e7c30909ef9700000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x54fc",
   "jp_len": 11,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "难道是……",
   "zh_hex": "15e866e82ae7b609090000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x5522",
   "jp_len": 8,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "艇长……？",
   "zh_hex": "15eb6bef340909050000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x555f",
   "jp_len": 11,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "……呀啊！！",
   "zh_hex": "150909e9c6e7c3ef97ef970000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x558c",
   "jp_len": 16,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "喂、没事吧！？",
   "zh_hex": "15e8bd02e7d8efb8e7d0ef9705000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x55b7",
   "jp_len": 14,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "啊……是、是的……！",
   "zh_hex": "15e7c30909e7b602e7b6e7b40909ef97000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x55c5",
   "jp_len": 16,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "这艘船、到底发生了什么事……？",
   "zh_hex": "15e7b9eb18ea0202e7d7e9b4e870ef8de7bae7dde7bdefb80909050000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x55f0",
   "jp_len": 17,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "好像是宇宙海盗袭来了",
   "zh_hex": "15e7c7e8e9e7b6e8bee8bfe91be9f3e9aeefcfe7ba0000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x561c",
   "jp_len": 11,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "宇宙……海盗……？",
   "zh_hex": "15e8bee8bf0909e91be9f30909050000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x565b",
   "jp_len": 10,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "呀啊啊！？",
   "zh_hex": "15e9c6e7c3e7c3ef9705000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x5687",
   "jp_len": 18,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "唔……！实力太悬殊了！！",
   "zh_hex": "15e81d0909ef97e87fefb0e86aec6ced7be7baef97ef97000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x5699",
   "jp_len": 24,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "我们明明只是非武装的运输舰{00}那帮家伙……！！",
   "zh_hex": "158be7bbef39ef39ef32e7b6e8f0e8ece98fe7b4e986e8b9e7d400e7b7e910e7dfe7fd0909060600000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x56cc",
   "jp_len": 6,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "啊……",
   "zh_hex": "15e7c309090000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x56ed",
   "jp_len": 8,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "怎么了！？",
   "zh_hex": "15e7f2e7bde7baef97050000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x5710",
   "jp_len": 10,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "那个、你看那边……",
   "zh_hex": "15e7b7e82802e7b8e7f6e7b7e89909090000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x5735",
   "jp_len": 6,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "！？",
   "zh_hex": "15ef97050000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x573b",
   "jp_len": 25,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "那不是MS吗！{00}怎么会对这种运输舰下手！？",
   "zh_hex": "15e7b7e7b5e7b61314e8020600e7f2e7bde7e2e7bee7b9e7d1e986e8b9e7d489ae0605000000000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x5754",
   "jp_len": 26,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "……不！现在不是说这些的时候！",
   "zh_hex": "150909e7b5ef97e82fef29e7b5e7b6e7ede7b9e8a4e7b4ef2dea39ef970000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x576e",
   "jp_len": 20,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "与其就这样白白送死……！！",
   "zh_hex": "15e832e8cfe7c5e7b9e7dae809e809e9baef6a0909ef97ef9700000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x57cf",
   "jp_len": 12,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "啊、等等！",
   "zh_hex": "15e7c302e826e826ef970000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x5806",
   "jp_len": 21,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "你、你……会驾驶MS吗？",
   "zh_hex": "15e7b802e7b80909e7e2e953e975efa7ef9ee80205000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x5843",
   "jp_len": 34,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "我只有作业用的执照、不过当个炮台应该{00}还行！",
   "zh_hex": "15efccef32e7cbef2feadaefb3e7b4e9fcea1a02e7b5ef36ef53e828e95aea16e873e89800e7f7efd6ef9700000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x586c",
   "jp_len": 15,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "你待在这儿太危险、快找地方躲起来……",
   "zh_hex": "15e7b8eaa8ef29e7b9eb7ce86ae935e93202e85fe9d2ef63efb1ea6fe847efcf0909000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x5896",
   "jp_len": 14,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "不、也带我一起去！",
   "zh_hex": "15e7b502e7c0e937efccefb6e847e7ebef97000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x58a4",
   "jp_len": 24,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "一个人留下来太不安了、而且、我……",
   "zh_hex": "15efb6e828efb2e98cef4defcfe86ae7b5e7fce7ba02e89ce99902efcc0909000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x58e0",
   "jp_len": 20,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "……知道了！那、到这边来！",
   "zh_hex": "150909e85ae82ae7ba06e7b702e7d7e7b9e899d90600000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x58f4",
   "jp_len": 8,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "唔……",
   "zh_hex": "15e81d0909000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x5917",
   "jp_len": 12,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "啊……我、我叫贝尔纳黛特",
   "zh_hex": "15e7c30909efcc02efcce8c1e857e7e1e882ea9ae7cf000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x5944",
   "jp_len": 18,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "我叫托比亚！{00}托比亚·阿罗纳克斯！！",
   "zh_hex": "158be8c1e7f4e825e7d60600e7f4e825e7d604e7d2e7ece882e7d5e7c80606000000000000000000000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x5956",
   "jp_len": 32,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "起飞会有点猛！{00}一定要抓紧了……贝尔纳黛特",
   "zh_hex": "15e847ea45e7e2e7cbe822ed87060087e867ef2ae962eaede7ba0909e857e7e1e882ea9ae7cf00000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x598a",
   "jp_len": 13,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "知道了……托比亚！",
   "zh_hex": "15e85ae82ae7ba0909e7f4e825e7d606000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x5a12",
   "jp_len": 11,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "哦……是MS吗？",
   "zh_hex": "15e9190909e7b6efa7ef9ee80205000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x5a4f",
   "jp_len": 12,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "原来如此、那家伙是……",
   "zh_hex": "15e8e4efcfe7f0e7ca02e7b7e7dfe7fde7b60909000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x5a76",
   "jp_len": 10,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "怎么了、金凯度？",
   "zh_hex": "15e7f2e7bde7ba02e902e95fe96d050000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x5a9b",
   "jp_len": 11,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "那家伙的对手……",
   "zh_hex": "15e7b7e7dfe7fde7b4e7beef660909000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x5aa6",
   "jp_len": 10,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "就由我来！！",
   "zh_hex": "15e7c5e8a6efccefcfef97ef97000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x5ad6",
   "jp_len": 11,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "托比亚……它来了！！",
   "zh_hex": "15e7f4e825e7d60909e978d9e7ba06060000000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x5b06",
   "jp_len": 28,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "管你是海盗还是什么的……想让我死在这{00}种地方……",
   "zh_hex": "15e93be7b8e7b6e91be9f3e7f7e7b6e7dde7bde7b40909e7e6e7f9efccef6aef29e7b900e7d1ef63efb109090000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x5b2c",
   "jp_len": 17,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "我才不会乖乖被你们杀掉！！",
   "zh_hex": "15efcce836e7b5e7e2e9a3e9a3e7f1e7b8e7bbe89be9d3ef97ef97000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x5b6e",
   "jp_len": 11,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "……太天真了！！",
   "zh_hex": "150909e86ae844e820e7baef97ef970000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x5baa",
   "jp_len": 10,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "呀啊啊啊！",
   "zh_hex": "15e9c6e7c3e7c3e7c3ef970000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x5bd9",
   "jp_len": 21,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "明、明明命中了、为什么……！？",
   "zh_hex": "15ef3902ef39ef39e853ef4ee7ba02e7c1e7dde7bd0909ef970500000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x5c1e",
   "jp_len": 8,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "唔……！",
   "zh_hex": "15e81d0909060000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x5c48",
   "jp_len": 12,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "怎么样……你打算怎么办？",
   "zh_hex": "15e7f2e7bde7da0909e7b8e7f5e889e7f2e7bde8ea050000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x5c6f",
   "jp_len": 13,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "怎、怎么办？",
   "zh_hex": "15e7f202e7f2e7bde8ea050000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x5c7c",
   "jp_len": 29,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "你们不是宇宙海盗吗！？{00}不打算杀了我们吗？",
   "zh_hex": "15e7b8e7bbe7b5e7b6e8bee8bfe91be9f3e802060500e7b5e7f5e889e89be7ba8be7bbe80205000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x5cbd",
   "jp_len": 17,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "你能选的路、有两条……",
   "zh_hex": "15e7b8e7c6e966e7b4e8d202e7cbe97de9d4090900000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x5ce9",
   "jp_len": 7,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "……诶？",
   "zh_hex": "150909eaf305000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x5d0b",
   "jp_len": 34,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "一条是、就这样回到地球、当作什么都没{00}发生过、守口如瓶",
   "zh_hex": "15efb6e9d4e7b602e7c5e7b9e7daef52e7d7ef63efd302ef53ef2fe7dde7bde840e7d800e870ef8def3602e8a8eabde7f0ee6b000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x5d6c",
   "jp_len": 12,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "而另一条则是……",
   "zh_hex": "15e89ce99befb6e9d4ea87e7b609090000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x5d9e",
   "jp_len": 8,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "……！？",
   "zh_hex": "150909ef97050000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x5dd7",
   "jp_len": 25,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "另一条是、和我们一起、去直面真相",
   "zh_hex": "15e99befb6e9d4e7b602e7d3efcce7bbefb6e84702e7ebe875e862e820e8b10000000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x5e16",
   "jp_len": 11,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "直面……真相",
   "zh_hex": "15e875e8620909e820e8b10000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x5e46",
   "jp_len": 20,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "艇、艇长！这到底是怎么回事……！？",
   "zh_hex": "15eb6b02eb6bef34ef97e7b9e7d7e9b4e7b6e7f2e7bdef52efb80909ef970500000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x5e7e",
   "jp_len": 24,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "哼……看来一切都被你看穿了啊、宇宙海{00}盗",
   "zh_hex": "15e8b30909e7f6efcfefb6ef3fe840e7f1e7b8e7f6ea7ee7bae7c302e8bee8bfe91b00e9f30000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x5eb8",
   "jp_len": 15,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "艇、艇长……！？",
   "zh_hex": "15eb6b02eb6bef340909ef97050000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x5f80",
   "jp_len": 7,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "……哼",
   "zh_hex": "150909e8b30000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x5fae",
   "jp_len": 16,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "一切都是为了杜加奇总统！！",
   "zh_hex": "1587ef3fe840e7b6e7c1e7bae8cbe854e904e881e92906060000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x5fe6",
   "jp_len": 18,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "什……！？战、战舰、还有MS！？",
   "zh_hex": "15e7dd0909ef9705ef2802ef28e7d402e7f7e7cbefa7ef9eef970500000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x6013",
   "jp_len": 31,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "所谓往返于地球与木星之间的运输舰、完{00}全是伪装",
   "zh_hex": "15e7fbe92be911eba8e879ef63efd3e832efa9ef69e7cde8fce7b4e986e8b9e7d402e87e00efb4e7b6eca7e98f0000000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x6032",
   "jp_len": 17,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "他们其实是木星帝国的武装船队",
   "zh_hex": "15e80ce7bbe8cfe87fe7b6efa9ef69e8f8efc4e7b4e8ece98fea02e7c90000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x605e",
   "jp_len": 9,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "木星帝国！？",
   "zh_hex": "15efa9ef69e8f8efc4ef970500000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x6082",
   "jp_len": 31,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "一边假装成温和的邻邦、一边虎视眈眈地{00}图谋侵略地球……",
   "zh_hex": "15efb6e899eb28e98fe837e9c0e7d3e7b4ed13efaa02efb6e899ec91e9d9ed8eed8eef6300eb2dea6eea46eb3def63efd30909000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x60a1",
   "jp_len": 18,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "那就是我们的敌人、木星帝国！",
   "zh_hex": "15e7b7e7c5e7b6efcce7bbe7b4e7e3efb202efa9ef69e8f8efc4ef9700000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x60da",
   "jp_len": 29,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "怎么样、你决定了吗？……已经见识过他{00}们真面目的你",
   "zh_hex": "15e7f2e7bde7da02e7b8e8abe867e7bae802050909ef3ae8b7e85ce92fef36e80c00e7bbe820e862efd4e7b4e7b800000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x613c",
   "jp_len": 7,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "托比亚……",
   "zh_hex": "15e7f4e825e7d609090000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x616f",
   "jp_len": 16,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "事到如今、还能怎么办……",
   "zh_hex": "15efb8e7d7e7f0efb902e7f7e7c6e7f2e7bde8ea0909000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x617f",
   "jp_len": 37,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "我才不会让木星帝国那种莫名其妙的家伙{00}对地球为所欲为！！",
   "zh_hex": "158be836e7b5e7e2e7f9d4b5e8f8a1e7b7e7d1eba0e8ace8cfecc7e7b4e7dfe7fd00e7bebf95e7c1e7fbeacbe7c106060000000000000000000000000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x61ca",
   "jp_len": 15,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "哼……胆子不小嘛、小子",
   "zh_hex": "15e8b30909edaee886e7b5e83ee93602e83ee88600000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x61f4",
   "jp_len": 22,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "别叫我小子！{00}我叫托比亚·阿罗纳克斯！！",
   "zh_hex": "15e7e5e8c18be83ee88606008be8c1e7f4e825e7d604e7d2e7ece882e7d5e7c80606000000000000000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x6225",
   "jp_len": 22,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "那么托比亚……你先暂时撤回先锋母舰",
   "zh_hex": "15e7b7e7bde7f4e825e7d60909e7b8b8e9ffef2de90a8cb8e967e9d5e7d4000000000000000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x6256",
   "jp_len": 7,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "诶……？",
   "zh_hex": "15eaf3090905000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x6278",
   "jp_len": 29,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "那边有适合你的机体、要打就用它去打！",
   "zh_hex": "15e7b7e899e7cbef41efc0e7b8e7b4e7e4ef4f02ef2ae7f5e7c5efb3e978e7ebe7f5ef9700000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x62b0",
   "jp_len": 11,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "好、好的！",
   "zh_hex": "15e7c702e7c7e7b4060000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x62e2",
   "jp_len": 19,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "金凯度……你、到底在打什么主意？",
   "zh_hex": "15e902e95fe96d0909e7b802e7d7e9b4ef29e7f5e7dde7bde954ef3c05000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x6310",
   "jp_len": 8,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "……谁知道呢",
   "zh_hex": "150909e923e85ae82ae9070000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x6318",
   "jp_len": 9,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "比起这个、扎比涅",
   "zh_hex": "15e825e847e7b9e82802e84be825eacf0000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x6321",
   "jp_len": 32,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "木星帝国那帮家伙、差不多也快等得不耐{00}烦了吧？",
   "zh_hex": "15efa9ef69e8f8efc4e7b7e910e7dfe7fd02e9c7e7b5e7e9e7c0e85fe826e80ae7b5ecfb00e95be7bae7d0050000000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x635c",
   "jp_len": 6,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "唔……",
   "zh_hex": "15e81d09090000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x637d",
   "jp_len": 15,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "就这样一举了结他们吧、扎比涅！",
   "zh_hex": "15e7c5e7b9e7da87ea21e7bae868e80ce7bbe7d002e84be825eacf060000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x63a7",
   "jp_len": 7,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "……明白了",
   "zh_hex": "150909ef39e809e7ba0000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x63d6",
   "jp_len": 12,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "金、金凯度先生……！",
   "zh_hex": "15e90202e902e95fe96def8bef8d0909ef970000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x63e2",
   "jp_len": 26,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "竟然连这种民用穿梭机都袭击、那些家伙{00}真是……",
   "zh_hex": "15ef2ce7efe86ee7b9e7d1ef38efb3ea7eeb8fe7e4e840e9aee7cc02e7b7e8a4e7dfe7fd00e820e7b609090000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x6417",
   "jp_len": 8,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "……看好了",
   "zh_hex": "150909e7f6e7c7e7ba0000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x641f",
   "jp_len": 18,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "快要露出马脚了",
   "zh_hex": "15e85fef2ae858efbee84feb68e7ba000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x6452",
   "jp_len": 7,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "诶……？",
   "zh_hex": "15eaf3090905000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x647e",
   "jp_len": 13,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "木星……帝国……！！",
   "zh_hex": "15efa9ef690909e8f8efc40909ef97ef970000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x64a6",
   "jp_len": 21,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "我们十字先锋真正的目的、",
   "zh_hex": "15efcce7bbea4ae980ef8be967e820ef3be7b4efd4e7b4020000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x64bb",
   "jp_len": 21,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "就是保护地球免遭他们的侵略！",
   "zh_hex": "15e7c5e7b6ea47e8e0ef63efd3eb7deb1ee80ce7bbe7b4ea46eb3def970000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x64d0",
   "jp_len": 11,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "上吧、托比亚！！",
   "zh_hex": "15b2e7d002e7f4e825e7d606060000000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x64fc",
   "jp_len": 11,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "是……是！！",
   "zh_hex": "15e7b60909e7b6ef97ef970000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x652e",
   "jp_len": 10,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "……出来了吗",
   "zh_hex": "150909efbeefcfe7bae802000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x655e",
   "jp_len": 17,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "你不要紧吧……托比亚？",
   "zh_hex": "15e7b8e7b5ef2aeaede7d00909e7f4e825e7d605000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x658a",
   "jp_len": 14,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "啊、别担心！",
   "zh_hex": "15e7c302e7e5e9fde82def970000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x6598",
   "jp_len": 27,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "我也一样、至少能为守护地球尽一份力！",
   "zh_hex": "15efcce7c0efb6e7da02e897eface7c6e7c1e8a8e8e0ef63efd3e8f2efb6ea22efb0ef9700000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x65bd",
   "jp_len": 11,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "……我是托比亚·阿罗纳克斯！",
   "zh_hex": "1509098be7b6e7f4e825e7d604e7d2e7ece882e7d5e7c8060000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x65c8",
   "jp_len": 16,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "海盗高达、出击！！",
   "zh_hex": "15e91be9f3e812ef2b02efbee7ccef97ef97000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x65fe",
   "jp_len": 11,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "你来了……托比亚！",
   "zh_hex": "15e7b8d9e7ba0909e7f4e825e7d606000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x6624",
   "jp_len": 30,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "我也是个男人！怎能就这样坐视不管！",
   "zh_hex": "15efcce7c0e7b6e828ea95efb2ef97e7f2e7c6e7c5e7b9e7daecc3e9d9e7b5e93bef9700000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x665d",
   "jp_len": 14,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "跟得上吧、托比亚？",
   "zh_hex": "15e973e80ab2e7d002e7f4e825e7d6050000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x6686",
   "jp_len": 24,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "啊！就算咬着不放、我也一定会跟上你！",
   "zh_hex": "15e7c3ef97e7c5e889edf5e86de7b5e86c02efcce7c0efb6e867e7e2e973ef4ce7b8ef9700000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x66b9",
   "jp_len": 11,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "好……上！",
   "zh_hex": "15e7c70909ef4cef970000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x66e5",
   "jp_len": 8,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "哦哦！！",
   "zh_hex": "15e919e919ef97ef970000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x671b",
   "jp_len": 27,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "这样一来、就打掉了木星帝国的一支尖兵{00}部队了",
   "zh_hex": "15e7b9e7daefb6efcf02e7c5e7f5e9d3e7baefa9ef69e8f8efc4e7b4efb6e883ee10ef9300ef70e7c9e7ba00000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x6751",
   "jp_len": 25,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "可这、也不过是壁虎断尾罢了",
   "zh_hex": "15e7c4e7b902e7c0e7b5ef36e7b6ee03ec91e982ebc0eaefe7ba00000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x676a",
   "jp_len": 11,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "他们的主力部队、可还没动……",
   "zh_hex": "15e80ce7bbe7b4e954efb0ef70e7c902e7c4e7f7e7d8ef3009090000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x679a",
   "jp_len": 14,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "不好！是别动队吗！！",
   "zh_hex": "15e7b5e7c7ef97e7b6e7e5ef30e7c9e802ef97ef970000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x67c3",
   "jp_len": 26,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "竟敢违抗杜加奇总统的蠢货！{00}给我消失吧！",
   "zh_hex": "15ef2ce8cdeab2e912e8cbe854e904e881e929e7b4e94beaf50600e8398be928e8a5e7d006000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x6802",
   "jp_len": 9,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "啧……！",
   "zh_hex": "15e9fa0909ef970000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x6832",
   "jp_len": 11,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "休想……！",
   "zh_hex": "15e90ee7e60909ef970000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x68c2",
   "jp_len": 14,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "那是……逃生舱！？",
   "zh_hex": "15e7b7e7b60909e8c2ef8debebef97050000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x6926",
   "jp_len": 7,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "托比亚！？",
   "zh_hex": "15e7f4e825e7d60605000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x6948",
   "jp_len": 9,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "回收！",
   "zh_hex": "15ef52e926ef970000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x6951",
   "jp_len": 29,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "就算是敌方的人、{00}也总不能见死不救吧！？",
   "zh_hex": "15e7c5e889e7b6e7e3d0e7b4b40200e7c0e881e7b5e7c6e85ca7e7b5e8cae7d00605000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x6996",
   "jp_len": 11,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "喂、你不要紧吧！？",
   "zh_hex": "15e8bd02e7b8e7b5ef2aeaede7d0ef9705000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x69bc",
   "jp_len": 9,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "……是的",
   "zh_hex": "150909e7b6e7b40000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x69e0",
   "jp_len": 6,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "！？",
   "zh_hex": "15ef97050000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x69e6",
   "jp_len": 9,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "是、是个女孩子！？",
   "zh_hex": "15e7b602e7b6e828efade956e886ef9705000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x6a0a",
   "jp_len": 6,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "啊……",
   "zh_hex": "15e7c309090000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x6a10",
   "jp_len": 21,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "我、我……偷偷潜上了那艘船……",
   "zh_hex": "15efcc02efcc0909ebb4ebb4eb3cef4ce7bae7b7eb18ea02090900000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x6a40",
   "jp_len": 13,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "喂、怎么了托比亚！？",
   "zh_hex": "15e8bd02e7f2e7bde7bae7f4e825e7d60605000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x6a68",
   "jp_len": 12,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "啊、是、是！",
   "zh_hex": "15e7c302e7b602e7b6060000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x6a74",
   "jp_len": 25,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "逃生舱里、坐着一个偷渡上船的女孩子…{00}…",
   "zh_hex": "15e8c2ef8debebef3102ecc3e86defb6e828ebb4ec27ef4cea02e7b4efade956e8860900090000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x6aa8",
   "jp_len": 9,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "……偷渡者？",
   "zh_hex": "150909ebb4ec27ef6e050000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x6acc",
   "jp_len": 9,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "总之……",
   "zh_hex": "15e881e7cd09090000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x6ad5",
   "jp_len": 20,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "她这样下去太危险、我先把她带回先锋女{00}王号！",
   "zh_hex": "15e88ee7b9e7daef4de7ebe86ae935e93202efccef8be81be88ee937ef52ef8be967efad00e884e833ef97000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x6b0e",
   "jp_len": 9,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "来吧……",
   "zh_hex": "15d9e7d00909000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x6b3e",
   "jp_len": 7,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "……谢谢你",
   "zh_hex": "150909e8b2e8b2e7b80000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x6b45",
   "jp_len": 20,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "啊……我、我叫贝尔纳黛特、贝尔纳黛特{00}·布里耶特",
   "zh_hex": "15e7c30909efcc02efcce8c1e857e7e1e882ea9ae7cf02e857e7e1e882ea9ae7cf00ef4be831ef31ea31e7cf000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x6b74",
   "jp_len": 13,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "……我、我叫托比亚·阿罗纳克斯",
   "zh_hex": "1509098b028be8c1e7f4e825e7d604e7d2e7ece882e7d5e7c8000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x6ba2",
   "jp_len": 9,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "谢谢你……托比亚",
   "zh_hex": "15e8b2e8b2e7b80909e7f4e825e7d60000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x6bd2",
   "jp_len": 11,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "贝尔纳黛特、是吗……",
   "zh_hex": "15e857e7e1e882ea9ae7cf02e7b6e8020909000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x6c02",
   "jp_len": 20,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "喂、托比亚！你在那儿发什么呆！！",
   "zh_hex": "15e8bd02e7f4e825e7d606e7b8ef29e7b7eb7ce870e7dde7bdedf40606000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x6c31",
   "jp_len": 18,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "啊！对不起、我这就回去！！",
   "zh_hex": "15e7c3ef97e7bee7b5e84702efcce7b9e7c5ef52e7ebef97ef970000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x6c6a",
   "jp_len": 16,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "哼……是十字先锋吗",
   "zh_hex": "15e8b30909e7b6ea4ae980ef8be967e80200000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x6c95",
   "jp_len": 30,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "再这样放着不管、恐怕会影响进攻地球的{00}作战……",
   "zh_hex": "15e80be7b9e7dae86ce86de7b5e93b02eb33e958e7e2ea8eecbfe892ef67ef63efd3e7b400ef2fef2809090000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x6cce",
   "jp_len": 22,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "……无妨、那些家伙不必担心",
   "zh_hex": "150909e7dce97f02e7b7e8a4e7dfe7fde7b5e860e9fde82d000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x6cff",
   "jp_len": 7,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "啊……？",
   "zh_hex": "15e7c30909050000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x6d21",
   "jp_len": 16,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "我早已布下了后手",
   "zh_hex": "15efcce963ef3ae831ef4de7bae7feef660000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x6d31",
   "jp_len": 12,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "早就安排好了……呵呵呵呵",
   "zh_hex": "15e963e7c5e7fcea67e7c7e7ba0909ef3def3def3def3d0000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x6d56",
   "jp_len": 19,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "那么贝尔纳黛特……你是木星那边的……",
   "zh_hex": "15e7b7e7bde857e7e1e882ea9ae7cf0909e7b8e7b6efa9ef69e7b7e899e7b40909000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x6d84",
   "jp_len": 19,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "……嗯、我是在木星圈出生的",
   "zh_hex": "150909e86502efcce7b6ef29efa9ef69e9fbefbeef8de7b4000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x6d97",
   "jp_len": 31,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "可我实在太想去地球了、才偷偷潜上了那{00}艘船……",
   "zh_hex": "15e7c4efcce87fef29e86ae7e6e7ebef63efd3e7ba02e836ebb4ebb4eb3cef4ce7bae7b700eb18ea020909000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x6dd1",
   "jp_len": 14,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "那么、你去过地球吗……",
   "zh_hex": "15e7b7e7bd02e7b8e7ebef36ef63efd3e80209090000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x6dfa",
   "jp_len": 15,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "还、没去过呢",
   "zh_hex": "15e7f702e7d8e7ebef36e907000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x6e09",
   "jp_len": 28,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "不过、我从在地球出生的母亲那儿、听过{00}很多关于地球的事……",
   "zh_hex": "15e7b5ef36028be88aef29bf95afb6e7b4e9d5e894e7b7eb7c02e8d1ef3600e981e7e9e8bbe879bf95e7b4a909090000000000000000000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x6e25",
   "jp_len": 31,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "各种各样的鸟儿和虫子、还有瀑布啊、{00}流凌啊、以及别的好多东西……",
   "zh_hex": "15e819e7d1e819e7dae7b4ec42eb7ce7d3eb6de88602e7f7e7cbe1dae831e7c30200ea2eede6e7c302e7f3e9cfe7e5e7b4e7c7e7e9e8bae7f8090900000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x6e44",
   "jp_len": 19,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "好多好多我从没见过的、不可思议的东西",
   "zh_hex": "15e7c7e7e9e7c7e7e9efcce88ae7d8e85cef36e7b402e7b5e7c4efcae8e3e7b4e8bae7f800000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x6e57",
   "jp_len": 18,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "所以、总有一天我也想去地球看看",
   "zh_hex": "15e7fbe7f302e881e7cbefb6e844efcce7c0e7e6e7ebef63efd3e7f6e7f600000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x6e69",
   "jp_len": 34,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "我想用自己的双脚、踏上地球的大地走一{00}走……这就是我的梦想",
   "zh_hex": "15efcce7e6efb3efb5e8c9e7b4eabceb6802ed0bef4cef63efd3e7b4efa5ef63e890efb600e8900909e7b9e7c5e7b6efcce7b4ea40e7e600000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x6ea6",
   "jp_len": 12,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "……一定会实现的、我保证",
   "zh_hex": "150909efb6e867e7e2e87fe82fe7b402efccea47eba30000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x6ecd",
   "jp_len": 9,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "谢谢你……托比亚",
   "zh_hex": "15e8b2e8b2e7b80909e7f4e825e7d60000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x6f05",
   "jp_len": 8,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "……！？",
   "zh_hex": "150909ef97050000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x6f35",
   "jp_len": 11,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "什么……！？",
   "zh_hex": "15e7dde7bd090906050000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x6f65",
   "jp_len": 10,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "……我也说不清",
   "zh_hex": "150909efcce7c0e7ede7b5e9950000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x6f6f",
   "jp_len": 22,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "只是、肯定是发生了什么事、这点错不了",
   "zh_hex": "15ef32e7b602e93de867e7b6e870ef8de7bae7dde7bdefb802e7b9e822e885e7b5e7ba0000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x6f85",
   "jp_len": 15,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "先锋母舰内部、出了什么状况……！",
   "zh_hex": "15b8e967e9d5e7d4e99acc02afe7bae7dde7bde98be8d0090906000000000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x6fae",
   "jp_len": 13,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "什么！？先锋母舰它！？",
   "zh_hex": "15e7dde7bd0605b8e967e9d5e7d4e97806050000000000000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x6fd6",
   "jp_len": 23,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "连拉米亚斯舰长您、也不知情吗？",
   "zh_hex": "15e86ee7c2e878e7d6e7c8e7d4ef34e83502e7c0e7b5e85ae88be802050000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x6fed",
   "jp_len": 31,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "刚才它以惊人的气势、冲出了基地……",
   "zh_hex": "15e8bce836e978e7f3ec6defb2e7b4e8ede8fd02e95eefbee7bae829ef630909000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x7027",
   "jp_len": 30,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "舰长、似乎并没有提交出击的申请……",
   "zh_hex": "15e7d4ef3402e944e933e957e7d8e7cbe821e861efbee7cce7b4ec7ce83a0909000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x7060",
   "jp_len": 18,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "能帮我查一下先锋母舰的去向吗？",
   "zh_hex": "15e7c6e9108beae98789b8e967e9d5e7d4e7b4e7eb9de80205000000000000000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x7072",
   "jp_len": 25,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "一旦查明位置、我们也立刻去追上他们",
   "zh_hex": "15efb6ebcdeae9ef39e834ea0e02efcce7bbe7c0e86be91fe7ebe8ddef4ce80ce7bb000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x708b",
   "jp_len": 18,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "总得先弄清楚到底发生了什么……",
   "zh_hex": "15e881e80aef8beac4e995ebd3e7d7e9b4e870ef8de7bae7dde7bd0909000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x70b8",
   "jp_len": 13,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "……是、明白了！",
   "zh_hex": "150909e7b602ef39e809e7baef970000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x70de",
   "jp_len": 11,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "……是预防者！？",
   "zh_hex": "150909e7b6ea5ae968ef6eef9705000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x7104",
   "jp_len": 24,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "你们！这究竟是怎么一回事！？",
   "zh_hex": "15e7b8e7bbef97e7b9e906ef2ce7b6e7f2e7bdefb6ef52efb8ef9705000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x711c",
   "jp_len": 26,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "竟然突然冲出去、还袭击运输船……",
   "zh_hex": "15ef2ce7efe8b6e7efe95eefbee7eb02e7f7e9aee7cce986e8b9ea02090900000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x715e",
   "jp_len": 11,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "核、核导弹……？",
   "zh_hex": "15e8f302e8f3ea4be9460909050000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x718e",
   "jp_len": 16,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "……他们、可是不择手段的",
   "zh_hex": "150909e80ce7bb02e7c4e7b6e7b5eaaaef66ea6be7b4000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x71b9",
   "jp_len": 17,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "他们？你是说、刚才那艘舰吗？",
   "zh_hex": "15e80ce7bb05e7b8e7b6e7ed02e8bce836e7b7eb18e7d4e8020500000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x71e5",
   "jp_len": 9,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "……是木星帝国",
   "zh_hex": "150909e7b6efa9ef69e8f8efc400000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x71ee",
   "jp_len": 13,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "我们真正的敌人……",
   "zh_hex": "15efcce7bbe820ef3be7b4e7e3efb209090000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x71fb",
   "jp_len": 25,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "打倒木星那误入邪路的领导者、格拉克斯{00}·杜加奇",
   "zh_hex": "15e7f5e848d4b5e7b7ea33e891ed12e8d2e7b4ea20ea4bad02e824e7c2e7d5e7c80004e8cbe854e904000000000000000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x7214",
   "jp_len": 21,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "这就是我们十字先锋的目的",
   "zh_hex": "15e7b9e7c5e7b6efcce7bbea4ae980ef8be967e7b4efd4e7b40000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x724e",
   "jp_len": 27,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "那么、刚才那个所谓木星帝国、就是你们{00}的……？",
   "zh_hex": "15e7b7e7bd02e8bce836e7b7e828e7fbe92befa9ef69e8f8efc402e7c5e7b6e7b8e7bb00e7b4090905000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x7284",
   "jp_len": 7,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "……是",
   "zh_hex": "150909e7b60000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x728b",
   "jp_len": 21,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "正是我们十字先锋真正的敌人",
   "zh_hex": "15ef3be7b6efcce7bbea4ae980ef8be967e820ef3be7b4e7e3efb200000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x72bb",
   "jp_len": 13,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "竟是企图侵略地球的人吗……",
   "zh_hex": "15ef2ce7b6ebdaeb2dea46eb3dbf95e7b4b4e8020909000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x72c8",
   "jp_len": 31,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "若不是亲眼见到刚才那一幕、实在难以置{00}信",
   "zh_hex": "15e7e7e7b5e7b6e894e90be85ce7d7e8bce836e7b7efb6ec1402e87fef29e866e7f3ea0e00e90f0000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x7308",
   "jp_len": 29,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "真没想到、木星的人们竟然企图侵略地球{00}……",
   "zh_hex": "15e820e7d8e7e6e7d702d4b5e7b4b4e7bbef2ce7efebdaeb2dea46eb3dbf95000909000000000000000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x734a",
   "jp_len": 30,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "察觉到这件事的人、就连在地球上恐怕也{00}没有几个",
   "zh_hex": "15ea8be8aee7d7e7b9e991efb8e7b4efb202e7c5e86eef29ef63efd3ef4ceb33e958e7c000e7d8e7cbeaa5e82800000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x7368",
   "jp_len": 28,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "虽自称帝国、实际不过是木星圈一座小小{00}的殖民地",
   "zh_hex": "15e8b8efb5ea01e8f8efc402e87fedc3e7b5ef36e7b6efa9ef69e9fbefb6ebc4e83ee83e00e7b4e8a9ef38ef63000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x7384",
   "jp_len": 22,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "毕竟、和地球联邦根本无法相提并论",
   "zh_hex": "15ea2cef2c02e7d3ef63efd3ef2eefaae9b8efa6e7dce84ee8b1e821e957e8dc0000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x73b5",
   "jp_len": 19,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "即便如此、还是要侵略地球吗？",
   "zh_hex": "15e855e8fae7f0e7ca02e7f7e7b6ef2aea46eb3def63efd3e802050000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x73e3",
   "jp_len": 21,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "或许、正因为是贫穷的殖民地……才会这{00}样吧",
   "zh_hex": "15e905e8a702ef3bef33e7c1e7b6eea5ed9be7b4e8a9ef38ef630909e836e7e2e7b900e7dae7d000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x7413",
   "jp_len": 32,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "他们在表面上只是家公社的殖民地里、暗{00}中推进着备战……",
   "zh_hex": "15e80ce7bbef29e9e7e862b2ef32e7b6e7dfe9a4ed96e7b4e8a9ef38bfef3102ea6a00c0eaabe892e86de877ef28090900000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x7433",
   "jp_len": 18,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "始终虎视眈眈地、等待着可乘之机",
   "zh_hex": "15e908e8e2ec91e9d9ed8eed8eef6302e826eaa8e86de7c4ebb1e7cde7e4000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x7445",
   "jp_len": 36,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "一边装出温和邻邦的样子、一边等待一举{00}打垮地球联邦的机会",
   "zh_hex": "15efb6e899e98fefbee9c0e7d3ed13efaae7b4e7dae88602efb6e899e826eaa8efb6ea2100e7f5ed43ef63efd3ef2eefaae7b4e7e4e7e2000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x7484",
   "jp_len": 21,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "在我们毫不知情之间、竟发生了这种事…{00}…",
   "zh_hex": "15ef29efcce7bbea0ae7b5e85ae88be7cde8fc02ef2ce870ef8de7bae7b9e7d1efb8090009000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x74a2",
   "jp_len": 28,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "……总之、这件事必须尽快做出应对才行",
   "zh_hex": "150909e881e7cd02e7b9e991efb8e860e9a2e8f2e85fe81cefbee873e7bee836efd60000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x74fa",
   "jp_len": 19,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "……不行、可不能让你们去应对……",
   "zh_hex": "150909e7b5efd602e7c4e7b5e7c6e7f9e7b8e7bbe7ebe873e7be0909000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x752e",
   "jp_len": 18,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "……那样的话、我可就为难了",
   "zh_hex": "150909e7b7e7dae7b4e81f02efcce7c4e7c5e7c1e866e7ba0000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x755b",
   "jp_len": 7,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "扎比涅！？",
   "zh_hex": "15e84be825eacf0605000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x7581",
   "jp_len": 7,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "好了……",
   "zh_hex": "15e7c7e7ba09090000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x7588",
   "jp_len": 21,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "诸位、都给我留在原地别动",
   "zh_hex": "15ea56e83402e840e839efcce98cef29e8e4ef63e7e5ef30000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x75b8",
   "jp_len": 10,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "贝拉……！",
   "zh_hex": "15e857e7c20909060000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x75e6",
   "jp_len": 23,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "这是什么意思、扎比涅？你打算背叛吗？",
   "zh_hex": "15e7b9e7b6e7dde7bdef3ca602e84be825eacf05e7b8e7f5e889e9e4ef43e802050000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x7618",
   "jp_len": 14,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "哈哈、背叛什么的……！",
   "zh_hex": "15e7e8e7e802e9e4ef43e7dde7bde7b40909ef97000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x7626",
   "jp_len": 19,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "背叛的是你、贝拉？",
   "zh_hex": "15e9e4ef43e7b4e7b6e7b802e857e7c2050000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x7639",
   "jp_len": 31,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "明明无心复兴宇宙巴比伦尼亚、却还打着{00}十字先锋的旗号……",
   "zh_hex": "15ef39ef39e7dce82de9eeeabae8bee8bfe85be825ea5be896e7d602eadfe7f7e7f5e86d00ea4ae980b8e967e7b4eb0be83309090000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x7697",
   "jp_len": 26,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "我的目的、从一开始就是让宇宙巴比伦尼{00}亚复活",
   "zh_hex": "158be7b4d5e7b402e88a87e7fae908e7c5e7b6e7f9e8bee8bfe85be825ea5be89600e7d6e9eee8d400000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x76b1",
   "jp_len": 25,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "为此、贝拉大人……还请您助我一臂之力",
   "zh_hex": "15e7c1e7ca02e857e7c2efa5efb20909e7f7e83ae835ea23efccefb6ee92e7cdefb0000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x76e5",
   "jp_len": 11,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "……你要我做什么？",
   "zh_hex": "150909e7b8ef2aefcce81ce7dde7bd050000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x770b",
   "jp_len": 12,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "把这艘先锋母舰……",
   "zh_hex": "15e81be7b9eb18b8e967e9d5e7d40909000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x7717",
   "jp_len": 26,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "连同预防者一起、向木星帝国投降",
   "zh_hex": "15e86ee85dea5ae968ef6eefb6e84702efc1efa9ef69e8f8efc4e948e943000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x774c",
   "jp_len": 26,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "你是说、要把我们卖给木星帝国吗！？",
   "zh_hex": "15e7b8e7b6e7ed02ef2ae81befcce7bbec4ce839efa9ef69e8f8efc4e802ef970500000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x7781",
   "jp_len": 27,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "对宇宙巴比伦尼亚来说、地球联邦同样是{00}该消灭的敌人……",
   "zh_hex": "15e7bee8bee8bfe85be825ea5be896e7d6d9e7ed02bf95ef2ed1e85de7dae7b600e898e928e8e1e7b4e7e3b40909000000000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x779c",
   "jp_len": 32,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "而这件事、就由他们来代劳！岂不正合我{00}意！",
   "zh_hex": "15e89ce7b9e991efb802e7c5e8a6e80ce7bbefcfe8e7ec4aef97eac3e7b5ef3befc0efcc00ef3cef970000000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x77fb",
   "jp_len": 15,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "再说、你也看到了吧？",
   "zh_hex": "15e80be7ed02e7b8e7c0e7f6e7d7e7bae7d0050000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x780a",
   "jp_len": 24,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "木星兵为了达成目的、连性命都豁得出去{00}……",
   "zh_hex": "15efa9ef69ef93e7c1e7baef2be837efd4e7b402e86ee951e853e840eba5e80aefbee7eb00090900000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x7822",
   "jp_len": 34,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "他们的做法、正与我们追求的新贵族主义{00}不谋而合",
   "zh_hex": "15e80ce7bbe7b4e81ce84e02ef3be832efcce7bbe8dde93ae7b4ef8ae930eb5ee954e8ce00e7b5ea6ee89cefc0000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x7844",
   "jp_len": 32,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "至于那些细微的差异、加入之后再一点点{00}改过来就好……",
   "zh_hex": "15e897e879e7b7e8a4eb9aeb58e7b4e9c7eb3202e854e891e7cde7fee80befb6e822e82200e9f0ef36efcfe7c5e7c7090900000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x787f",
   "jp_len": 12,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "扎比涅、你这家伙……！！",
   "zh_hex": "15e84be825eacf02e7b8e7b9e7dfe7fd0909060600000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x78a6",
   "jp_len": 8,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "呵……",
   "zh_hex": "15ef3d0909000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x7912",
   "jp_len": 13,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "一路辛苦了",
   "zh_hex": "15efb6e8d2ea58e9e6e7ba0000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x791f",
   "jp_len": 32,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "感谢你、把这条『宇宙世纪路线』一路玩{00}到了最后",
   "zh_hex": "15e87de8b2e7b802e81be7b9e9d40ce8bee8bfe83ceb99e8d2e9160defb6e8d2e97000e7d7e7bae8c5e7fe0000000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x793f",
   "jp_len": 31,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "另外、隆德·贝尔队的战斗、在此暂告一{00}段落……",
   "zh_hex": "15e99be8f702ed16e82cef4be857e7e1e7c9e7b4ef28e7ff02ef29e7cae9ffe8e5efb600ea6be92a0909000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x795e",
   "jp_len": 37,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "不过游戏本身仍可继续、之后也请你尽情{00}玩下去",
   "zh_hex": "15e7b5ef36ea94ea3eefa6e88deab9e7c4e9d6e9ad02e7cde7fee7c0e83ae7b8e8f2e88b00e970ef4de7eb00000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x7983",
   "jp_len": 39,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "此外、为通关了本路线的你、还准备了特{00}别关卡",
   "zh_hex": "15e7cae8f702e7c1ef59e8bbe7baefa6e8d2e916e7b4e7b802e7f7e87ae877e7bae7cf00e7e5e8bbe8010000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x79aa",
   "jp_len": 33,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "那是、与一直在别处奋战的大天使队进行{00}的特别演习",
   "zh_hex": "15e7b7e7b602e832efb6e875ef29e7e5e903ef46ef28e7b4efa5e844e83fe7c9e892efd600e7b4e7cfe7e5ea2feab6000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x79cb",
   "jp_len": 37,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "与他们交手、检验一下你亲手培养的部队{00}实力、也不错",
   "zh_hex": "15e832e80ce7bbe861ef6602ee40ea99efb6ef4de7b8e894ef66edfeec0be7b4ef70e7c900e87fefb002e7c0e7b5e885000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x79f0",
   "jp_len": 37,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "在自由对战中选择『特殊演习』、即可与{00}他们一战",
   "zh_hex": "15ef29abe8a6e7beef28c0e966eaaa0ce7cfed7bea2feab60d02e855e7c4e83200e80ce7bb87ef280000000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x7a15",
   "jp_len": 36,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "……那么、就请在这部『SD高达G世代{00}DS』中",
   "zh_hex": "150909e7b7e7bd02e7c5e83aef29e7b9ef700cef9eef96e812ef2beed1e83ce8e700ef96ef9e0def4e0000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x7a39",
   "jp_len": 21,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "继续尽情游玩、直到最后吧",
   "zh_hex": "15e9d6e9ade8f2e88bea94e97002e875e7d7e8c5e7fee7d000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x7ab2",
   "jp_len": 31,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "一路以来、谢谢你愿意陪伴我这个不够可{00}靠的舰长",
   "zh_hex": "15efb6e8d2e7f3efcf02e8b2e8b2e7b8e961ef3cef42ea72efcce7b9e828e7b5e920e7c400e8c7e7b4e7d4ef3400000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x7ad1",
   "jp_len": 30,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "这条『平成高达路线』、就到此结束了",
   "zh_hex": "15e7b9e9d40ce887e837e812ef2be8d2e9160d02e7c5e7d7e7cae868e895e7ba000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x7aef",
   "jp_len": 26,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "当然、虽然我们预防者的战斗已经结束…{00}…",
   "zh_hex": "15ef53e7ef02e8b8e7efefcce7bbea5ae968ef6ee7b4ef28e7ffef3ae8b7e868e89509000900000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x7b09",
   "jp_len": 38,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "……但游戏本身还能继续、之后也请继续{00}享受游戏哦",
   "zh_hex": "150909e7dbea94ea3eefa6e88de7f7e7c6e9d6e9ad02e7cde7fee7c0e83ae9d6e9ad00ec06e8c8ea94ea3ee919000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x7b2f",
   "jp_len": 36,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "还为通关了本路线的你、准备了全新的关{00}卡哦",
   "zh_hex": "15e7f7e7c1ef59e8bbe7baefa6e8d2e916e7b4e7b802e87ae877e7baefb4ef8ae7b4e8bb00e801e9190000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x7b53",
   "jp_len": 27,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "那是和我们分头作战、与提坦斯及新吉翁{00}交战过的……",
   "zh_hex": "15e7b7e7b6e7d38be7bbcde92eef2fef2802e832e821e843e7c8e9cfef8ae7d9ee8800e861ef28ef36e7b409090000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x7b6e",
   "jp_len": 19,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "……隆德·贝尔队的特别演习哦",
   "zh_hex": "150909ed16e82c04e857e7e1e7c9e7b4e7cfe7e5ea2feab6e9190000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x7b81",
   "jp_len": 38,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "在自由对战中选择『特别演习』、就能和{00}他们一战哦",
   "zh_hex": "15ef29efb5e8a6e7beef28ef4ee966eaaa0ce7cfe7e5ea2feab60d02e7c5e7c6e7d300e80ce7bbefb6ef28e91900000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x7ba7",
   "jp_len": 14,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "请你务必去挑战看看哦",
   "zh_hex": "15e83ae7b8e94fe860e7ebeae7ef28e7f6e7f6e919000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x7bb5",
   "jp_len": 36,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "……那么、下面请看『SD高达G世代{00}DS』",
   "zh_hex": "150909e7b7e7bd0289e862e83ae7f60c1411e812ef2beed1e83ce8e70011140d0000000000000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x7bd9",
   "jp_len": 28,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "『自由对战的战火！冲锋陷阵吧、大天使{00}！！』",
   "zh_hex": "150cefb5e8a6e7beef28e7b4ef28e8daef97e95ee967eaf9eb48e7d002efa5e844e83f00ef97ef970d000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x7c5a",
   "jp_len": 16,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "我是主天使号舰长、娜塔尔·巴基露露中{00}佐",
   "zh_hex": "15efcce7b6e954e844e83fe833e7d4ef3402e7eae945e7e1ef4be85be829e858e858ef4e00efba000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x7c6a",
   "jp_len": 34,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "首先、请允许我向你一路以来出色的指挥{00}、致以敬意",
   "zh_hex": "15ef40b802e83aecade8a78b9de7b887e8d2e7f3d9afe89fe7b4e8c0e9490002ea32e7f3ee38ef3c0000000000000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x7c8c",
   "jp_len": 34,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "多亏有你的协助、我们才得以奋战到最后{00}一刻",
