  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x7cae",
   "jp_len": 22,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "这条『对手路线』、就到此结束",
   "zh_hex": "15e7b9e9d40ce7beaee8d2e9160d02e7c5e7d7e7cae868e89500000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x7cc4",
   "jp_len": 25,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "当然、虽然我们主天使队的战斗已就此结{00}束……",
   "zh_hex": "15ef53e7ef02e8b8e7efefcce7bbe954e844e83fe7c9e7b4ef28e7ffef3ae7c5e7cae86800e895090900000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x7cdd",
   "jp_len": 36,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "不过游戏本身仍可继续、之后也希望你能{00}继续玩下去",
   "zh_hex": "15e7b5ef36ea94ea3eefa6e88deab9e7c4e9d6e9ad02e7cde7fee7c0e87be965e7b8e7c600e9d6e9ade970ef4de7eb000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x7d01",
   "jp_len": 43,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "自由对战之后仍可继续、另外、只要选择{00}『特别演习』……",
   "zh_hex": "15efb5e8a6e7beef28e7cde7feeab9e7c4e9d6e9ad02e99be8f702ef32ef2ae966eaaa000ce7cfe7e5ea2feab60d090900000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x7d2c",
   "jp_len": 30,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "便能与隆德·贝尔、预防者进行联合演习",
   "zh_hex": "15e8fae7c6e832ed16e82cef4be857e7e102ea5ae968ef6ee892efd6ef2eefc0ea2feab60000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x7d4a",
   "jp_len": 37,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "我相信、以你的实力、与他们一战也定能{00}取得胜利",
   "zh_hex": "158be8b1e90f02e7f3e7b8e7b4e87fda02e832e80ce7bb87ef28e7c0e867e7c600e987e80ae8dbe82e000000000000000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x7d6f",
   "jp_len": 36,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "……那么、就请在这部『SD高达G世代{00}DS』中",
   "zh_hex": "150909e7b7e7bd02e7c5e83aef29e7b9ef700cef9eef96e812ef2beed1e83ce8e700ef96ef9e0def4e0000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x7d93",
   "jp_len": 16,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "今后也祝你武运长久、奋战到底",
   "zh_hex": "15efb9e7fee7c0ed97e7b8e8ece986ef34e9db02ef46ef28e7d7e9b4000000"
  }
 ]
}
